{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"91a9718987","title":"给孙燕的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"360efc9217","index":0,"year":1957,"month":12,"day":17,"articleId":"91a9718987"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji38","name":"毛泽东全集第38卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/38-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji38":{"comments":[{"id":"28bc860ef3","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"91a9718987","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"孙燕，学名孙佩君。她的母亲陈玉英1926年冬到毛泽东和杨开慧家里当保姆。1930年10月随杨开慧一起被国民党反动派速捕，在获中同敌人作了不屈的斗争。"}],"contents":[{"id":"925f7cc717","type":"title","text":"给孙燕的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"91a9718987"},{"id":"28bc860ef3","type":"paragraph","text":"配君同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"91a9718987"},{"id":"d3d70cdcb4","type":"paragraph","text":"来信收到。我同意你的意见，不去乡村。你母亲年已六十，不能劳动，当然不宜下放。你年小，你母亲需要照料，可以不去。但此事应由党作决定。你可持此信和你母亲一道，去湖南省委统战部，找那里的负责同志谈一谈，请他作出决定。我这封信只是建议，不是决定。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"91a9718987"},{"id":"6cfac5089c","type":"paragraph","text":"问你母亲和你好！","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"91a9718987"},{"id":"8740b731d9","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"91a9718987"},{"id":"36695fca99","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五七年十二月十七日","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"91a9718987"},{"id":"4358ed2f39","type":"paragraph","text":"去统战部时，可把你母亲照顾杨开慧同志的历史谈一下，使那里的同志了解情况。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"91a9718987"}],"page":{"id":"2a92edae16","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"91a9718987","start":380,"end":380}}}},"__N_SSG":true}